    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Quickly make a jacket, tent or outerwear repair and say goodbye to holes and tears with Tenacious Tape Gear Patches. This versatile black nylon repair tape requires no heat or sewing skills. Simply peel the backing and apply to the surface with pressure; it won’t peel or lift even after a wash. The various shapes and sizes make jacket repair fun and personal. Stick it on almost anything made of synthetic fabrics including rainwear, ski pants, gloves and backpacks without the gooey residue (not for cotton, denim, or natural fabrics). When sewing and ironing isn’t an option, use Tenacious Tape Gear Patches for a unique and speedy repair that lasts all year long.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Gear Aid Tenacious Tape Gear Patches for Outdoor Wear (Many Styles and Sizes)</h2>\n  <p>Quickly make a jacket, tent or outerwear repair and say goodbye to holes and tears with Tenacious Tape Gear Patches. This versatile black nylon repair tape requires no heat or sewing skills. Simply peel the backing and apply to the surface with pressure; it won’t peel or lift even after a wash. The various shapes and sizes make jacket repair fun and personal. Stick it on almost anything made of synthetic fabrics including rainwear, ski pants, gloves and backpacks without the gooey residue (not for cotton, denim, or natural fabrics). When sewing and ironing isn’t an option, use Tenacious Tape Gear Patches for a unique and speedy repair that lasts all year long.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Fix a tent, jacket or outerwear fast with peel-and-stick Tenacious Tape Gear Patches; no heat required, just remove backing and apply</li>\n    <li>Stick on to synthetic fabrics including nylon, vinyl, GORE-TEX® fabric, and polyester; patches are backed with ultra-strong adhesive (not for cotton, denim, or natural fabrics)</li>\n    <li>Use these washable patches to repair holes and tears on outdoor gear including backpacks, sleeping bags, and gloves; won’t peel back over time</li>\n    <li>Cover up stains or personalize your puffy coat and gear with fun shapes for water bottles, helmets and luggage</li>\n    <li>Packaging may vary</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/25108_green_main.jpg/patches_parent_1.jpg\" alt=\"Quickly make a jacket, tent or outerwear repair and say goodbye to holes and tears with Tenacious Tape Gear Patches\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
